      <description>&lt;p&gt;To reach a level in a class you will need to have at least the amounts shown in the table below.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Decimals will not count towards your level so if you have 74.9 in a skill it will count as 74.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To reach higher than level 4 you will need either skill items or get tomes to raise your skill caps.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can also find stat potions to raise your stat caps.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
